@FlightStateService_HostAddress = http://localhost:5001

### List flights (paginated)
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/flights?pageNumber=1&pageSize=10

### List flights filtered by status
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/flights?status=departed

### Search flights by status
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/flights/search?status=depart

### Search flights by partial flight ID
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/flights/search?flightId=a1b2c3d4

### Get flight details (replace with a real flight ID from list response)
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/flights/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Get flight event history
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/flights/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/history

### Operational metrics
GET {{FlightStateService_HostAddress}}/api/metrics
